1
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,400
Dad.

2
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:26,560
Xingxing needs a complete family.

3
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,039
I plan to bring him back,

4
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,740
treat him as my own,

5
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,280
and take care of him with Zhixia.

6
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:34,610
You've completely ruined the reputation

7
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:36,840
of generations of the Lu family.

8
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,640
To raise a child of unknown origin

9
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:41,120
as your own son!

10
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,490
If word gets out,

11
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:45,000
what will others think of the Lu family?

12
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,720
Xingxing is Zhixia's child.

13
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,000
He is very sensible.

14
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,660
I don't care if he is sensible.

15
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,660
As long as he doesn't have the Lu family's blood,

16
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:55,160
he will never step foot in this house.

17
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,240
And

18
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,960
if you dare to get back together with Shen Zhixia

19
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,720
and bring that child back here,

20
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,920
don't call me your father ever again.

21
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,160
The heir to the Lu family.

22
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,919
You absolutely cannot be held back by a woman

23
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:09,919
with a burden.

24
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,960
I will never allow this.

25
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,010
Don't even think about it anymore.

26
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:31,520
Chairman Lu hasn't relented.

27
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,920
He will.

28
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,600
Release a piece of news for me.

29
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,480
What news?

30
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,640
About how I, Lu Jingheng,

31
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:38,320
abandoned my wife and children.

32
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,280
How can we do that?

33
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,560
Isn't that throwing yourself under the bus?

34
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,600
The stronger the fire, the better.

35
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:45,329
Things will only be easier if it burns the old man.

36
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,050
What's wrong with you guys?

37
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,079
Coach Shen is here.

38
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:57,960
Coach Shen.

39
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,000
Look at the news!

40
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,960
Lu Jingheng abandoning his wife and child is trending.

41
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,160
What exactly is going on?

42
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,040
Exactly.

43
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,440
It says Mr. Lu doesn't care about you and the child,

44
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:06,160
and makes you live in the gym's storage room.

45
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,160
Is it true?

46
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:09,040
How could it be true?

47
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,520
It's not true.

48
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,960
He didn't abandon his wife and child.

49
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,280
I left on my own.

50
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:14,700
Here she is! Hurry!

51
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,440
Ms. Shen! Ms. Shen!

52
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,640
Ms. Shen!

53
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,360
Is it true that Mr. Lu abandoned you?

54
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,600
Are you living in this boxing gym now

55
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,920
because Mr. Lu refuses to pay for your living expenses?

56
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:22,440
Ms. Shen!

57
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:24,280
Will you sue Mr. Lu over the child support?

58
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,320
Yeah, Ms. Shen.

59
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,500
Quiet down, everyone.

60
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,040
Mr. Lu is here.

61
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,040
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

62
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,120
Mr. Lu, please explain.

63
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,520
Is the news true or false?

64
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:39,280
In the past, I haven't been a good father,

65
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,640
nor a good husband.

66
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,320
I made Zhixia and the child suffer,

67
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,130
living in a storage room all this time.

68
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,540
I didn't take care of them in time.

69
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,840
It is all my fault.

70
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,680
From now on,

71
00:03:57,680 --> 00:04:00,680
I will raise the child well together with Zhixia.

72
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:03,760
The Lu family will always be their home,

73
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,240
and I won't let them suffer anymore.

74
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,280
Mr. Lu, explain a bit more.

75
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,040
Yes, Mr. Lu.

76
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,770
Then why did such news come out?

77
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,480
Thank you, everyone.

78
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:13,800
Mr. Lu.

79
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,480
Excuse me.

80
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,280
Mr. Lu.

81
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,880
Mr. Lu, please say a few more words.

82
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:17,200
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

83
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:19,200
Answer this question again, Mr. Lu.

84
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,480
Wait, Mr. Lu.

85
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,360
You haven't answered the question.

86
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,520
Please answer the question, Mr. Lu.

87
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,640
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

88
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:35,880
Dad, I know

89
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:38,320
you don't want Zhixia and Xingxing to come back.

90
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:40,120
But the news has already spread.

91
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,840
Going back on our word now

92
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:44,159
will only make the Lu family's reputation worse.

93
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,080
I'm doing this

94
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,960
only for the family's image.

95
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,159
Let them stay.

96
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,260
Thank you, Dad.

97
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,720
Come, Xingxing.

98
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,720
Come to Mommy.

99
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,400
Just treat this as me going back to my old job.

100
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,680
I'll play along with you one more time.

101
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,680
Once the news blows over,

102
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,160
we're still getting a divorce.

103
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,840
So, we'll follow the old rules.

104
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:15,000
We live together but sleep in separate rooms.

105
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,260
Your room is next door.

106
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,340
You're overthinking.

107
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,160
Of course we'll sleep in separate rooms.

108
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,360
Then why haven't you left?

109
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,620
None of your business.

110
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,680
The kid asked me to stay.

111
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:30,480
Mommy, I want to sleep with Uncle Lu.

112
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,409
His stories are very interesting.

113
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,760
Be good, Xingxing. I'll read to you.

114
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:38,080
But Uncle is more patient.

115
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:40,280
Every time you get halfway through,

116
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:42,120
you fall asleep.

117
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,520
Xingxing.

118
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,800
Uncle needs to go back and sleep.

119
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,200
He is sleeping next door.

120
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,680
Uncle Lu, stay.

121
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,560
I'll sleep in the middle.

122
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:55,080
With Mom and Uncle Lu here,

123
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,780
I'm not afraid of the dark.

124
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,840
Xingxing.

125
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,600
I want to sleep with Uncle Lu.

126
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,440
I really want to.

127
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:04,560
Uncle Lu, sleep here with us.

128
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,440
Only for tonight.

129
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,000
Of course.

130
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,040
His friends forgave him.

131
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:33,120
Later, they lived together happily.

132
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:45,130
You should move back tomorrow.

133
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:48,480
This bed is too crowded for three people.

134
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:53,480
I'll have someone bring a bigger bed tomorrow.

135
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:57,920
So Xiao Xingxing won't squeeze you when turning over at night.

136
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,320
Who wants to share a big bed with you?

137
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,040
You're right about everything.

138
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,100
I'll listen to you.

139
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,800
Go to sleep.

140
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:23,560
If Mommy doesn't eat, Xingxing won't eat either.

141
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,120
Xingxing is copying you.

142
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,760
Mommy is eating, so Xingxing will eat too.

143
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,000
Here.

144
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,400
What a good kid.

145
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,040
Eat a little more.

146
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,200
Xingxing,

147
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:29,680
what kind of story do you want to hear today?

148
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:33,960
Xingxing wants to hear the story of Boxing Superman again today.

149
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,960
Then do you remember

150
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,960
where we left off last time?

151
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,919
I remember.

152
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,919
We left off where Boxing Superman lives in

153
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:45,800
a really big blue glass house.

154
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:48,200
Every time he beats the bad guys,

155
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:53,120
strawberry-flavored smoke comes out of the glass house.

156
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:03,200
Then today we'll tell Xingxing...

157
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:11,760
Honey.

158
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,360
He's asleep.

159
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,400
He's asleep.

160
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,570
He played all day and got tired.

161
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:19,000
Here, have a taste

162
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,980
before the noodles get soggy.

163
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,800
You made this?

164
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,800
How is it?

165
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:36,330
It's delicious.

166
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,680
Eat more.

167
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,440
Are you that touched?

168
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,560
Not exactly.

169
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:57,440
I just feel

170
00:09:57,440 --> 00:10:00,360
you've been working hard taking care of Xingxing and me lately.

171
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,320
He starts kindergarten tomorrow.

172
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,780
You won't have to revolve around us anymore.

173
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,290
I still have some work to do.

174
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:24,090
Get some rest early.

175
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:26,080
I'll head back after I clean up.

176
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:26,720
Okay.

177
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,930
It's delicious.

178
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,240
I'll make it for you again next time.

179
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:32,880
Okay.

180
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,760
Is it that delicious?

181
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,400
It's so salty.

182
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,700
Xiaoxingxing.

183
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:18,720
We are going to school now, okay?

184
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,320
If Xiaoxingxing cries later,

185
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,320
you'll comfort him,

186
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,760
and I'll distract him.

187
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:27,320
That way, he can get used to it.

188
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:29,960
Why are you so sure the kid will cry, Mr. Lu?

189
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:32,840
Do you remember what I taught you yesterday?

190
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:35,440
Press this to call if anything happens.

191
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,320
Right. You are very smart.

192
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,200
At school.

193
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,400
If you miss your mom,

194
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:41,400
just press this.

195
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,560
If a teacher speaks too loudly,

196
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:44,960
or a kid takes your toy,

197
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,130
you must press this.

198
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:50,840
Mom, I want to play with the other kids.

199
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:51,720
Okay.

200
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,040
Mr. Lu, you worry too much.

201
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:54,200
Kids only think about playing.

202
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,440
Why would he cry?

203
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,000
Mr. Lu.

204
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,260
This is Mr. Han from Little Star's class.

205
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,200
Good morning, Mr. and Mrs. Lu.

206
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,120
My surname is Han.

207
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:12,680
I will be responsible for taking care of Little Star from now on.

208
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,720
Hello, Mr. Han.

209
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,400
Hello, Mr. Han.

210
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,880
Sorry to trouble you.

211
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,560
The third page here

212
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:20,200
lists Little Star's allergens.

213
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:22,400
He must not have mangoes or celery.

214
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:22,880
Okay.

215
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:25,440
The seventh page is about his nap habits.

216
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,960
He must hold this dinosaur doll

217
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:28,840
to fall asleep.

218
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,360
Okay.

219
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,560
My personal phone number is on the last page.

220
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:32,880
It's on 24 hours a day.

221
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:35,160
Contact me anytime if anything happens.

222
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,280
Okay, Mr. Lu.

223
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,080
Rest assured.

224
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:39,940
We will definitely take good care of Xiaoxingxing.

225
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:43,560
Teacher, the butterfly is so pretty.

226
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,480
If Xiaoxingxing cries,

227
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:49,640
give her the strawberry cookies we prepared.

228
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,080
They must be cut into small pieces.

229
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,120
There can't be any sharp corners.

230
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,080
Ms. Butterfly,

231
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:55,800
can you take Xingxing to play on the slide?

232
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,160
Of course.

233
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,600
Great!

234
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,200
Sorry for the trouble, Ms. Han.

235
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,040
Not a problem.

236
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:07,740
Xingxing is going to play on the slide with Miss Butterfly.

237
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:09,200
Listen to your teacher.

238
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,920
Why isn't he crying?

239
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,920
He has been wanting to come to kindergarten since last week.

240
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:19,320
You are overthinking it.

241
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,240
Bye, Mom.

242
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:25,600
Bye, Dad.

243
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:31,080
Goodbye.

244
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:39,240
I... I have things to do this afternoon.

245
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,640
I need to go to the office.

246
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:41,880
Pick him up early.

247
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:43,690
Be the first one.

